 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n入面有教</blockquote><br />\n入面你肯定教晒mistake, misrepresentation, economic duress, undue influence, unconscionability, frustration, express terms, implies terms, exemption clauses等等？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有見過"},{"pid":"51616f229e1be36505ef5d7f08ea157af4cf62e4","tid":129480,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T03:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基本上一個一字頭/二字頭既合同法<br />\n就係讀緊50%基本法律知識加埋50%丹寧爵士既見解<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHigh Tree case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce87a73c24f57ee3d9d37c2aee6aeeaa3e8e4314","tid":129480,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藥房 case 呢<br />\nbtw llb contract law 都玩過<br />\n好好玩<br />\n記 300 個 case 名到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下？<br />\n<br />\n重點係咪買同埋用 smoke ball 個動作等於 acceptance ???"},{"pid":"f601ca4b8a456d6c251c737cde804ed840eddf38","tid":129480,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:17:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鏗哥有組未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc20e527ed0f1ed7aa7413504d056172c60f24b","tid":129480,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>藥房 case 呢<br />\nbtw llb contract law 都玩過<br />\n好好玩<br />\n記 300 個 case 名到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下？<br />\n<br />\n重點係咪買同埋用 smoke ball 個動作等於 acceptance ???</blockquote><br />\n之後又講咩 invitation to treat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d219d98f8d342d33e5974a674be0f560fce48fc7","tid":129480,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:22:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>藥房 case 呢<br />\nbtw llb contract law 都玩過<br />\n好好玩<br />\n記 300 個 case 名到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下？<br />\n<br />\n重點係咪買同埋用 smoke ball 個動作等於 acceptance ???</blockquote><br />\nSmoke ball個case係unilateral offer，因為有intention to be legally bound<br />\nAcceptance係另一樣野，單案係講有人做到報紙入面要求嘅野，acceptance by conduct所以unilateral offer無得被revoked"},{"pid":"a062f6a2e0173e1dc226a2c4895bade43e9d347a","tid":129480,"uid":85860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:26:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Year one 讀 contract law<br />\n走曬堂，臨考前幾日先溫......<br />\n搞到宜家要追gpa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAnyway, 其實lee mason 本contract law係幾深入淺出幾雞精，仲比其他lecturer話如果淨睇依本textbook 實得c range <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLee Mason本野好流...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n臨考前先溫到宜家都未睇過本書3成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c074f5496c147c301096f3ba19c27e0c7ad463","tid":129480,"uid":60538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:45:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>藥房 case 呢<br />\nbtw llb contract law 都玩過<br />\n好好玩<br />\n記 300 個 case 名到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下？<br />\n<br />\n重點係咪買同埋用 smoke ball 個動作等於 acceptance ???</blockquote><br />\n之後又講咩 invitation to treat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ninvitation to treat 你睇藥房case<br />\n你係超市拎起一件貨去俾錢<br />\n好多人以為係超市 offer 你一個價錢問你 accept 唔 accept.<br />\n呢個 invitation to treat 就係講緊 超市只係 比個機會你去offer 超市賣比你<br />\n最後係超市 accept 你個 offer<br />\n所以超市標錯價佢理論上係無問題"},{"pid":"ce35811bc790898c9b3e5affa61fbf0fc7c7776a","tid":129480,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T05:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>藥房 case 呢<br />\nbtw llb contract law 都玩過<br />\n好好玩<br />\n記 300 個 case 名到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下？<br />\n<br />\n重點係咪買同埋用 smoke ball 個動作等於 acceptance ???</blockquote><br />\n之後又講咩 invitation to treat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ninvitation to treat 你睇藥房case<br />\n你係超市拎起一件貨去俾錢<br />\n好多人以為係超市 offer 你一個價錢問你 accept 唔 accept.<br />\n呢個 invitation to treat 就係講緊 超市只係 比個機會你去offer 超市賣比你<br />\n最後係超市 accept 你個 offer<br />\n所以超市標錯價佢理論上係無問題</blockquote><br />\n巴打們點睇呢本書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/135517_e6a7d5994fb66296ce7ed4315e0ccdd7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F135517_e6a7d5994fb66296ce7ed4315e0ccdd7.jpg&h=d23c1fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}